I think to myself, "Oh great, am i delusional? Thats great, right before my first day of college im talking to bees. Just at that moment, the bug repeats again. "Your Majesty, what are your orders? I looked straight at the bee in the eyes and didnt know what to say. "You talking to me?". Was the first thing I could think of. The bee says nothing. Then a couple seconds later the bee repeats "Your Majesty, what are your orders?". "If you dont tell me your orders than I am going to have to follow you

I think to myself, "Oh great, am i delusional? Thats great, right before my first day of college im talking to bees. Just at that moment, the bug repeats again. "Your Majesty, what are your orders? I looked straight at the bee in the eyes and didnt know what to say. "You talking to me?". Was the first thing I could think of. The bee says nothing. Then a couple seconds later the bee repeats "Your Majesty, what are your orders?". "If you dont tell me your orders than I am going to worry about you". Why would this little tiny bee be worried about me, i dont get it? I just stood there looking at it and then i started laughing. "Your already my best friend and I can barely even see you." I said. "Your Majesty, please give me a name so that I know what to identify you as". Jor

I think to myself, "Oh great, am i delusional? Thats great, right before my first day of college im talking to bees. Just at that moment, the bug repeats again. "Your Majesty, what are your orders? I looked straight at the bee in the eyes and didnt know what to say. "You talking to me?". Was the first thing I could think of. The bee says nothing. Then a couple seconds later the bee repeats "Your Majesty, what are your orders?". "If you dont tell me your orders than I am going to worry about you". Why would this little tiny bee be worried about me, i dont get it? I just stood there looking at it and then i started laughing. "Your already my best friend and I can barely even see you." I said. "Your Majesty, please give me a name so that I know what to identify you as". Jordan, i told the bee. "Hey bee, you want to get out of here and hang out. Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

I looked up into the sky. Am i just hearing things. I look around the park and dont see anyone else talking to bugs, so i must just be sick or tired maybe. I think to myself, "Oh great, am i delusional? Thats great, right before my first day of college im talking to bees. Just at that moment, the bug repeats again. "Your Majesty, what are your orders? I looked straight at the bee in the eyes and didnt know what to say. "You talking to me?". Was the first thing I could think of. The bee says nothing. Then a couple seconds later the bee repeats "Your Majesty, what are your orders?". "If you dont tell me your orders than I am going to worry about you". Why would this little tiny bee be worried about me, i dont get it? I just stood there looking at it and then i started laughing. "Your already my best friend and I can barely even see you." I said. "Your Majesty, please give me a name so that I know what to identify you as". Jordan, i told the bee. "Hey bee, you want to get out of here and hang out. You dont have to grand any of my orders, just be cool". I said. "Your Majesty, is that an order? To be cool?". asked the bee. I looked at the bee and said "dont call me majesty, call me JOrd
